<h1>Michiana's home for bounce house rentals</h1>
<p>Playtime Jumpers is a family owned and operated inflatable bounce house
rental company. Located between Elkhart and Granger, our service areas include:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Bristol</li>
  <li>Nappanee</li>
  <li>Granger</li>
  <li>Niles</li>
  <li>Edwardsburg</li>
  <li>Osceola</li>
  <li>Elkhart</li>
  <li>South Bend</li>
  <li>Middlebury</li>
  <li>Wakarusa</li>
  <li>Mishawaka</li>
</ul>
<p>We specialize in providing bounce houses, jumpers, bouncer/slides and 
slip-n-slides for you backyard parties. We are your #1 source for familiy fun
parties, family reunions, company picnics or church events. Let us provide your
children with hours of safe & active fun at your next event.</p>

<h3>Quality, safe, and affordable fun for all</h3>
<p>We provide only quality, affordable inflatable bouncy castles. We are a
family-owned and operated company looking forward to providing your friends and
family a safe but eventful party or event. For all your party needs, we can
provide a fun and exciting addition. Great customer service along with a great
bouncer design guarantee a top notch party.</p>
